pages.text:
About
Serving quality food and drinks since 2017 on Marco Island. Come enjoy our indoor and outdoor seating, island vibe, happy hour, dinner, and after-dinner drinks. Watch the Eagles or Phillies games in our special environment - we're a proud Phillies bar. 2 Shea's Salty Dog is a peaceful retreat by the sunny coast, perfect for escaping a busy life. You can relax on the patio and enjoy delicious grouper and drinks while soaking in the laid-back island vibe at 2 Shea's.
Can I make a reservation?
We do not take reservations or call ahead seating.
When is Happy Hour?
Our happy hour is 7 days a week 2 pm-5 pm. Please take a look at our happy hour menu under the menus tab!
Will you show the NFL package?
Yes! We have your game! However, we only offer our big-screen TV when games are aired on Peacock.
Are dogs allowed?
Yes but only on our outside patio! Your fur babies are welcome and appreciated!
Do you Deliever?
We do not offer a delivery service. You are more than welcome to place a take-out order. Take a look at our menu and give us a call!
